    "description": "<p>Move up to your Speed then make a Melee Martial Attack vs PD</p><p>1 Slashing</p><ul><li><p><strong>(+1) Savage Cuts: </strong>Physical Save.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target begins Bleeding. While Bleeding from this, the target can’t remove Bleeding by regaining HP.</p></li></ul></li><li><p>(+1) Sunder: Physical Save.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target gains Physical Vulnerability (1) for 1 Round.</p></li></ul></li></ul><p><em><strong>System Tip:</strong> Use on demand macro to gain Move Points.</em></p>",
